dmdba\n</code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"安装数据库\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93\" aria-label=\"安装数据库 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装数据库</h4>\n<p>使用上一步创建新建的用户登录，执行数据库安装</p>\n<pre><code>mkdir /mnt/cdrom\nmount /dev/cdrom /mnt/cdrom\nchmod a+rx dmdbms-8.2-1.x86_64.rpm\nsudo rpm -ivh dmdbms-8.2-1.x86_64.rpm\n</code></pre>\n<pre><code>sudo ./dminit PATH=/var/dmdbms PAGE_SIZE=16\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"安装和配置nacos\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEnacos\" aria-label=\"安装和配置nacos permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装和配置Nacos</h3>\n<h4 id=\"前提\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90\" aria-label=\"前提 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 